To add WPCF Option Fields:
(for User):

1. Filter array of setting fields with WPCF_Setting_Fields.
    i.e. array('OPTION_NAME' => '<input name="OPTION_NAME" type="text" />');

2. Filter option names with WPCF_Option_Names.
    i.e. array('OPTION_NAME' => 'Option Fancy Name (Label)')

3. (if necessary) Filter posted data with WPCF_Posted_Settings.
    i.e. array('OPTION_NAME' => 'Option Value')

(for Developer):
1. add value(s) in _initialize_option_names
2. (if necessary) add process in _filter_setting_fields
3. (if necessary) add process in _filter_posted_settings